name: My Dress-Up
overview: My Dress Up features: Dress-Up yourself and your friends Practice your fashion creativity or hold a Dress-Up party Save your dress-up design in your wardrobe or send to your friends Design your own top (Blouse, T-shirt etc) Use photos from your My Make-Up friends for a full make-over Chat with your My Make-Up and My Secret Diary friends 6 wardrobes (space for 96 outfits), 14 clothing categories (up to 150 items in each) 112 colours
